data.description: Cute 3 bedroom 2 bath home located SW of Fallon on 6.04 acres, adjacent to BLM land.    A 24x24 shop with power and located right outside the shop additional power to hookup to an RV. Property has plenty of room for all those toys. partially fenced out back. TCID permit available for additional irrigation  Buyer agent to verify through TCID. Stove in the kitchen is not included in the sale however seller will replace with another stove.
